---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
---

<Base title="About">
  <div class="about">
    <h2>About SkillRanker</h2>

    <p>
      SkillRanker is an AI-powered ranking platform for Claude Code Agent Skills.
      It automatically discovers, evaluates, and ranks skills from GitHub and other
      sources to help you find the best tools for your workflow.
    </p>

    <h3>How it works</h3>
    <ol>
      <li><strong>Discovery</strong> &mdash; GitHub API search, awesome-lists, and web scraping find new skills daily</li>
      <li><strong>Evaluation</strong> &mdash; Hard metrics (maintenance, docs, completeness, adoption, structure) scored deterministically</li>
      <li><strong>AI Enrichment</strong> &mdash; Claude analyzes each skill for quality, usefulness, novelty, and generates summaries</li>
      <li><strong>Publishing</strong> &mdash; Rankings exported as JSON, static site built with Astro, deployed via GitHub Pages</li>
    </ol>

    <h3>Scoring</h3>
    <table>
      <thead>
        <tr><th>Component</th><th>Weight</th><th>What it measures</th></tr>
      </thead>
      <tbody>
        <tr><td>Maintenance</td><td>20%</td><td>Commit recency, releases, contributors, issue ratio</td></tr>
        <tr><td>Documentation</td><td>15%</td><td>SKILL.md quality, README, code examples, structure</td></tr>
        <tr><td>Completeness</td><td>15%</td><td>References, scripts, examples, templates</td></tr>
        <tr><td>Adoption</td><td>10%</td><td>Stars, forks, watchers (log-scaled)</td></tr>
        <tr><td>Structure</td><td>10%</td><td>License, tests, CI/CD, topics, repo age</td></tr>
        <tr><td>AI Quality</td><td>10%</td><td>Code/doc quality, clarity (AI-assessed)</td></tr>
        <tr><td>AI Usefulness</td><td>10%</td><td>Practical value for developers (AI-assessed)</td></tr>
        <tr><td>AI Novelty</td><td>10%</td><td>Uniqueness, not a rehash (AI-assessed)</td></tr>
      </tbody>
    </table>

    <h3>Open Source</h3>
    <p>
      This project is open source.
      <a href="https://github.com/skillranker-ai/skillranker">View on GitHub</a>
    </p>
  </div>
</Base>

<style>
  .about {
    max-width: 800px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .about h2 {
    font-size: 2rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .about h3 {
    margin-top: 2rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    font-size: 1.3rem;
  }

  .about p, .about li {
    color: var(--text-muted);
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  .about ol {
    padding-left: 1.5rem;
  }

  .about table {
    width: 100%;
    border-collapse: collapse;
    margin-top: 1rem;
  }

  .about th, .about td {
    text-align: left;
    padding: 0.5rem 0.75rem;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
  }

  .about th {
    color: var(--text);
    font-weight: 600;
  }

  .about td {
    color: var(--text-muted);
  }
</style>
